'''Domain Paasar''' was a [[Domain]] among the [[Warrior caste]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. During the [[Defense of Mon Calamari (Yuuzhan Vong War)|Defense of Mon Calamari]], their vessels were redirected to [[Contruum/Legends|Contruum]], to eventually reinforce [[Coruscant/Legends|Yuuzhan'tar]].<ref name="TUF">''[[The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force]]''</ref>

